# ChangeLog for sys-boot/grub-legacy
# Copyright 1999-2009 Gentoo Foundation, Copyright 2009 Funtoo Technologies; Distributed under the GPL v2

  11 Mar 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org> grub-legacy-0.97-r11: move
  to unstable for eventual unmasking; add dep on sys-apps/coreboot-1.4.1 which
  will support the new grub-legacy disk structure (/boot/grub-legacy/)

*grub-legacy-0.97-r11 (10 Mar 2010)

  10 Mar 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org> +grub-legacy-0.97-r11:
  New bug fix release - sed to get grub-install-legacy to call the right
  things. Needs testing.

*grub-legacy-0.97-r10 (03 Feb 2010)

  03 Feb 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org>
  +grub-legacy-0.97-r10.ebuild: renaming utilities with -legacy suffix and
  moving /lib/grub to /lib/grub-legacy to avoid conflicts and confusion.

*grub-0.97-r9 (02 Jan 2009)

  02 Jan 2009; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org> +grub-0.97-r9.ebuild:
  Ext4 funtime for grub-0.97 series. Remember to reinstall it in your MBR.
